name.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Private Dependency Graph extension for GitHub

short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Resolves private dependencies/dependents in your GitHub organization.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Are you missing private dependencies in GitHub?

The Private Dependency Graph extension resolves private dependents and dependencies in your GitHub account or organization.

✅ Set and forget
The dependency data is automatically synced every time a repository changes.

🔐 Privacy focused
Team members can only resolve private dependencies if they have read access to the repository. You have control and observability over the data we store.

📍 All your repos in a single place
Explore all your private dependencies in the web interface.

🔧 Integrated into GitHub's UI
Private dependency data is also shown on GitHub

🚀 More features coming soon!

Privacy Policy - https://topology.conformal.link/privacy-policy
